              "translation": "It is the Boundless, the Akaalpurakh, who is not subjected to births and deaths. (66)",
              "additional_information": {}
            }
          },
          "Punjabi": {
            "Dr. Ganda Singh": {
              "translation": "ਸ਼ਮ੍ਹਾ ਸੌ ਸੌ ਵਾਰ ਤੇਰੇ ਤੋਣ ਕੁਰਬਾਨ ਜਾ ਰਹੀ ਹੈ ।",
              "additional_information": {}
            }
          }
        }
